d to decide on the pricing model. I'm recommending the tiered plan we discussed last week.\r\n\r\nALEX: Let's go with the tiered pricing. Sarah, can you send the final pricing doc to the team by Friday?\r\n\r\nSARAH: Will do.\r\n\r\nJAMES: One more thing — the landing page copy still needs approval. Who's handling that?\r\n\r\nALEX: That's on me. I'll get it reviewed and approved before Wednesday.\r\n\r\nSARAH: Perfect. I think that covers everything.\r\n\r\nALEX: Agreed. Let's wrap up. Good meeting everyone.", "document_id": "doc_7b9c6c1f"}
